description: Xmet Inc., a mineral exploration company, acquires, explores, and develops mineral properties in Canada. It focuses on exploration of gold and graphite deposits in Quebec and Ontario. It holds interests in the Blackflake property located in northern Ontario, Canada; and Grasset gold, copper, and zinc property, which consists of 114 contiguous exploration licenses totaling an area of 7,040 hectares located to the west of Matagami, Quebec. Xmet Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Alexander G. Stewart B.A., BA, J.D.
